  <title>Food Quality Monitoring System </title>
<subsection xml:id="subsec-Introduction-food">
  <title>Introduction</title>
  <p>
    Food is the main source of energy for Human. Quality of the food is more important and also it is mandatory to maintain the safety and hygiene of the food to keep the food fresh and edible. There are different parameters to determine the decomposition of food, they are temperature, humidity and bacterium present in the food. When the temperature of the food is between 40F-140F the level of ethanol gas will be higher, then it is said to be a decomposed food .Table 2.5.1, illustrates the components required for experiment is listed with its purpose.it Monitors the food and prevents the food from decomposition. It saves people from food poisoning. In this experiment learners will learn about monitoring of food quality using Arduino UNO. 
  </p>
</subsection>
