  <subsubsection xml:id="subsubsec-DHT11-sensor">
    <title>DHT11 sensor </title>
    <p>
      DHT11 sensor detects both temperature and humidity present in the environment. This type of sensor is blended with NTC to measure temperature and it has an 8-bit micro controller to display the serial data. This sensor is built in such a way to detect both temperature and humidity in a single sensor. It is easy to interface with micro controller. Data pin is called as out pin can be used for both Analog and Digital. It can measure the temperature between 0 degree Celsius to 50 degrees celsius. The sensor has three pins 5V, GND and out pin. Operating voltage of the sensor is 2.5v to 5V.  LM135 sensor measures only the room tempertaure of the environment. Here DHT11 is used because it can measure both temperature and humidity.
    </p>
